properties.value: Vyre noble clothing are a set of clothing that is required to be worn to access the bank and shops within Darkmeyer. content:
Vyre noble clothing are a set of clothing that is required to be worn to access the bank and shops within Darkmeyer. It is scented with the blood of a vampyre noble to help blend in with the vampyres, which makes Vyrewatch Sentinels unaggressive and NPCs less hostile towards the player.

A vyre noble top, legs and shoes are created during the quest Sins of the Father. Should players lose this disguise, they can reclaim a set from the chest in the Old Man Ral's house Trapdoor.

Players can buy a greater variety of vyre noble clothing at the Darkmeyer Seamstress, which will also work as a disguise. However, they must be wearing the clothing when buying from the shop.

The original set of vyre noble clothing can be stored in an armour case of a player-owned house costume room.
